    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Pierce your <strong>sweet potatoes </strong>with a fork, and add them to a large heat-proof bowl covered with <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Cook in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 5-7 min or until slightly softened</p>",
