    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>softened</strong> <strong>sweet potatoes</strong> to a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>ground coriander</strong> and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 15 min or until the skins are crispy</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
