    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>yoghurt dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
