    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>baked</strong> <strong>sweet potatoes</strong> from the oven after the initial 15 min and carefully slice in half lengthways</p><p>Crumble <strong>half</strong> your<strong> goats' cheese</strong> (save the rest for later!) over the sweet potatoes with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and return the tray to the oven for a final 4-5 min or until the goats' cheese has slightly melted – these are your <strong>goats' cheese loaded sweet potatoes</strong></p>",
