    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> salad</strong> on plates with the <strong>crunchy spiced chickpeas</strong>, and <strong>roasted onion</strong> over the top</p><p>Top with the <strong>goats' cheese loaded sweet potatoes</strong> and crumble the <strong>remaining goats' cheese </strong>all over</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>yoghurt dressing</strong> on top and sprinkle over the <strong>pomegranate seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
